OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FThe family of a little girl from West
OL,7,FCumbria who is waiting for a heart
OL,8,Ftransplant is urging people to talk
OL,9,Fabout organ donation.
OL,11,FPoppy Lambert, who will turn 2 in
OL,12,FJuly, was born with a Tetralogy of
OL,13,FFallot (TOF), a serious heart
OL,14,Fcondition requiring surgery.
OL,16,FIn December, just before Christmas,
OL,17,Fshe underwent major open heart
OL,18,Fsurgery, which was supposed to be a
OL,19,Froutine procedure.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FHowever, complications followed and
OL,7,Ffor the past 4 months Poppy has relied
OL,8,Fon a Berlin heart (an external
OL,9,Fmechanical heart pump), while she
OL,10,Fwaits for a donor.
OL,12,FThe little girl has faced multiple
OL,13,Fsurgeries, a valve replacement, a
OL,14,Fsmall stroke which impacted her right
OL,15,Fside plus complications with breathing
OL,16,Fwhich led to her having a tracheostomy.
OL,18,FDoctors at the Freeman Hospital in
OL,19,FNewcastle have told the family that
OL,20,Fthe only thing that can save their
OL,21,Fchild's life is a heart transplant.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FHer mum, Becca Lambert, said: "It's a
OL,7,Fhorrible circle. A day doesn't go past
OL,8,Fwhere we don't think about the fact
OL,9,Fthat another family's got to lose
OL,10,Ftheir child in order for our child to
OL,11,Flive.
OL,13,F"We just pray and hope that people
OL,14,Funderstand that they're doing a
OL,15,Fselfless thing in giving our child
OL,16,Flife."
OL,18,FInitial treatments and surgery were
OL,19,Funable to fix the problems with
OL,20,FPoppy's heart and the family say they
OL,21,Fare now living from day to day.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FIn the UK, children can only receive a
OL,7,Fheart transplant at the Great Ormond
OL,8,FStreet Hospital (GOSH) in London or at
OL,9,Fthe Freeman Hospital in Newcastle.
OL,11,FUp to 35 heart transplants are carried
OL,12,Fout on children each year in the UK,
OL,13,Faccording to the NHS Blood and
OL,14,FTransplant service. But the waiting
OL,15,Ftime for children can be twice as long
OL,16,Fas adults because of the difficulties
OL,17,Fin finding a matching heart donor.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FA heart for Poppy could come from
OL,7,Fanywhere in the UK but also
OL,8,Fpotentially from as far afield as
OL,9,FEurope.
OL,11,FIn a twist of fate, poppy's mum worked
OL,12,Ffor the NHS in transplant services
OL,13,Fbefore Poppy was born and she says she
OL,14,Fhas always understood the need for
OL,15,Forgan donations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777554669
OL,3,CNew heart needed for Cleator Moor
OL,4,Ctoddler
OL,6,FShe added, "I always promoted organ
OL,7,Fdonation and blood donation because I
OL,8,Funderstood that it helped a lot of
OL,9,Ffamilies. But being on the other side
OL,10,Fof it has opened my eyes to the extent
OL,11,Fof how much it actually helps families
OL,12,Fin different situations."
OL,14,FPeople have donated nearly 19 thousand
OL,15,Fpounds to help support the family
OL,16,Ffinancially on a GoFundMe page - But
OL,17,Fthe most important donation for them
OL,18,Fwill be the one that saves their
OL,19,Fdaughter's life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
